INSERT INTO youtube_videos (
    youtube_video_id,
    youtube_channel_id,
    title,
    description,
    category_id,
    live_broadcast_content,
    published_at,
    views,
    likes,
    favorites,
    comments,
    duration,
    is_live,
    tags
)
VALUES (
    '${youtube_id}',
    '${youtube_channel_id}',
    '${title}',
    '${description}',
    '${category_id}',
    '${live_broadcast_content}',
    '${published_at}',
    ${views},
    ${likes:isEmpty():ifElse("CAST(NULL AS INTEGER)", ${likes})},
    ${favorites:isEmpty():ifElse("CAST(NULL AS INTEGER)", ${favorites})},
    ${comments:isEmpty():ifElse("CAST(NULL AS INTEGER)", ${comments})},
    '${duration}',
    ${is_live},
    '${tags_string}'
);
